{"tid":1234074,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"關於下一步行動","createTime":"2019-06-17T00:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T01:02:54.000Z","uid":149723,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d02fdc2558c90444269c19b13391de6308299aa3","tid":1234074,"uid":149723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:29:24.000Z","msg":"首先希望和理非同勇武派唔好再為尋晚發生嘅事<br />\n而對對方存有不信任嘅感覺<br />\n大家都係香港人 每一件事都係為香港而做 只不過係方式唔同<br />\n我係受 無敵比亞路 巴打所啟發先整合呢個po出嚟<br />\n<br />\n捉緊鬼/冇目標/悲觀既你入一入黎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233821\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233821</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>宜家溫和派就要set個deadline比政府回應民眾訴求<br />\n等日後勇武派既行動出師有名唔再係「鳩衝」<br />\n亦都比所有同路人有個明確目標 驅散無力感<br />\n政府既唔回應唔係我地輸 而係我地行動升級既理據</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同時希望大家花少少時間睇下 舒而 巴打嘅見解<br />\n<br />\n一晚玩撚完<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cPvowS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cPvowS</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>而家係雨傘初期咁嘅狀態<br />\n1. 好多市民支持<br />\n2. 黑警冇佈防唔清場<br />\n3. 政府唔回應一味死拖<br />\n4. 和理非同勇武又開始互屌捉鬼<br />\n5. 開始有好多未經証實的消息周圍傳<br />\n<br />\n目的<br />\n1. 等你地自己鬼打鬼<br />\n2. 消耗, 遊行三罷咩都好, 睇死你地唔頂得幾耐<br />\n3. 民氣隨時間消散<br />\n<br />\n輕鬆清場秋後, 香港人又輸一仗<br />\n好擔心歷史又重演<br />\n<br />\n有人話咁快就話可能會輸係悲觀<br />\n我諗重點係而家冇方向<br />\n同雨傘一樣<br />\n好大班有心人但大家都唔撚知可以點做<br />\n<br />\n所以而家要傾嘅係到底點撚樣做先有效<br />\n純和理非佔領=雨傘=失敗<br />\n純勇武=招人口實+所謂暴動+傷亡+坐監=旺角=失敗<br />\n純三罷=香港人好撚現實, 不了=失敗<br />\n<br />\n只有三樣一齊做先有可能成功<br />\n但所謂大和解兄弟爬山各有各做<br />\n大家根本欠缺信任<br />\n好難成功<br />\n<br />\n咁點先算成功<br />\n1. 撤回<br />\n2. 放人<br />\n3. 冇暴動<br />\n4. 黑警濫權<br />\n5. 下台<br />\n二百萬人底線個個唔同<br />\n如果佢同你deal應承是但一樣其他不了<br />\n收唔收貨點先收貨係要攞共識<br />\n<br />\n如果要deal要攞共識搵邊個做?<br />\n係我地唔需要大台<br />\n你見民陣搞三罷都搞到咁就明<br />\n但要談判總要搵代表<br />\n有正當性有正式民意授權(選票)嘅只係得議員<br />\n今次有啲議員嘅表現係令人意想不到<br />\n不過呢個根本係佢地本職份內事<br />\n只係我地習慣咗啲議員嘅質素<br />\n<br />\n我覺得有咩可以做<br />\n係叫泛民議員代我地去談判<br />\n乘著二百萬的勢去逼政府回應<br />\n唔撚理佢地用咩方法點樣逼<br />\n我剩係知議員有權力及特權條例buff保護<br />\n佢地再賣港嘅<br />\n得<br />\nIF WE BURN YOU BURN WITH US<br />\n你唔撚洗指意再做議員<br />\n我票投建制全世界一穫熟反正已經冇得救<br />\n大家一齊攬炒<br />\n<br />\n建制議員都唔好忽略<br />\n個個龜縮? 唔回應? <br />\n反對二百萬市民的睇法?<br />\n你愈割蓆我愈要拉返你班仆街一齊<br />\n唔好以為同林鄭割咗就唔關你事<br />\n你唔肯主動見市民咁市民唯有直接搵你<br />\n<br />\n上面冇提金融貿易戰中美關係台灣大選<br />\n唔知有咩可以係對外/國際層面可以做<br />\n求補充</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當中<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>係叫泛民議員代我地去談判<br />\n乘著二百萬的勢去逼政府回應<br />\n唔撚理佢地用咩方法點樣逼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個所謂將行動升級嘅方法就用 時也命也運也 巴打開嘅po<br />\n<br />\n今日 禮賓府 定 警總？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cPwBOS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cPwBOS</a><br />\n<br />\n我個人認為圍禮賓府係正確亦都係唯一做法<br />\n不過幾時圍係一個值得討論嘅地方 <br />\n今日可能太粗之過急<br />\n我地要依賴泛民方面嘅大團體 表示不滿意616政府作出嘅回應<br />\n然後再set個deadline 要政府喺deadline前做到  舒而 巴打提到嘅目標<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>1. 撤回<br />\n2. 放人<br />\n3. 冇暴動<br />\n4. 黑警濫權<br />\n5. 下台</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n否則就行動升級 之後再圍禮賓府將會更加出師有名<br />\n請大家盡快討論 否則只會辜負依家喺出面嘅人/畀人拉咗嘅勇武派/犧牲咗嘅烈士<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\nTLDR:<br />\n1. 泛民方面嘅大團體表示不滿意616政府作出嘅回應<br />\n2. Set deadline <br />\n3. 做唔到就將行動升級 圍禮賓府<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"66c3763561cc6d51df92c2eea8e4f5e9eaf9c742","tid":1234074,"uid":149723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:35:25.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5cdf96342d59ab911e2d89f8727f4defabaab69","tid":1234074,"uid":149723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:37:12.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5fb44bb3a5304d35e36f42083cdcf9704b321c","tid":1234074,"uid":149723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:39:13.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c9575d3eaf31325a43ad06db98c2383344dc109","tid":1234074,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:40:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4ed34ba9f64f349656bba08f311b9c5e9c50219f","tid":1234074,"uid":149723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:40:46.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de6685c7f06c911dd1483874024a39162025b16e","tid":1234074,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:41:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9c7e670db1f5847352683ce1ff33a00f3f74f0","tid":1234074,"uid":149723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:44:09.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39151ac0bca845460cab403042acd9f09247aa9","tid":1234074,"uid":149723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:46:49.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce5c61e77890e395f06b341c6cce5941437df35","tid":1234074,"uid":50901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:47:16.000Z","msg":"訴求不變 繼續接力"},{"pid":"a9acb51ce07c6ebea2e57d49083db944011a9fb0","tid":1234074,"uid":149723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:49:54.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f0d6b25428c74490ac8df4b30d100d36198ee2","tid":1234074,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:50:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有無人幫手整poster /長輩圖方便文宣！！！唔可以輕易俾香港人忘記！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 未撤回&quot;送中/逃犯條例&quot;<br />\n2. 未切查警察濫用武力、濫權、濫捕<br />\n3. 612 依然被定性為&quot;暴動&quot;, 想秋後算帳示威者<br />\n4. 未釋放被捕示威者<br />\n5. 林鄭未下台"},{"pid":"5c9b3386e4352cbd184e5d0c06310b32301f5509","tid":1234074,"uid":100714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:53:05.000Z","msg":"贊成"},{"pid":"cbd09d4c8c115c097169a021aa9e127722b60ef7","tid":1234074,"uid":149723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:53:16.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3e8543938ff66cd973cc3fd98733246bbeebe3","tid":1234074,"uid":149723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:56:02.000Z","msg":"我愛香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582cca19a26a5d97069ac5445ce27e73238ade36","tid":1234074,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:58:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66f18c03d10939f316fa8013e03b745c090803a1","tid":1234074,"uid":149723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:02:54.000Z","msg":"雖然時間有啲倉促<br />\n不過既然大家已經決定咗<br />\n咁推熱門嗰個就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[行動升級]10：00 轉戰禮賓府<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cPyaGS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cPyaGS</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}